entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Jasha, the Imperial captain at the fort overlooking Bestine, is looking for local's supporting the rebellion. He wanted you to collect ID cards from any Rebels you defeated. You got a number of ID cards and turned the information over to Jasha.. He wanted you to collect ID cards from any Rebels you defeated. entries.journal_entry_description: The Alliance is gaining more supporters with each passing day. The Empire has hired you to discover which families on Tatooine are supplying the Alliance with new recruits. Hunt down Rebels and compile a list of all those from Tatooine.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The Imperials want you to find out which Tatooine families are supporting the terrorists. By taking out terrorists in the hills and searching them for Tatooine identity cards you will be able to compile a list for Imperial Intelligence.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Well done. I will pass this information on to our counter-intellegence people. They will start survaillence of these person's families.
